#. module: cyllo_crm
#: model:mail.template,body_html:cyllo_crm.email_template_activity_assigned
msgid ""
"<div style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; line-height: 1.6; color: #333;\">\n"
"                    <div style=\"border-bottom: 2px solid #007bff; padding-bottom: 10px; margin-bottom: 20px;\">\n"
"                        <h2 style=\"color: #007bff; margin: 0;\">Activity Assigned on Lead</h2>\n"
"                    </div>\n"
"\n"
"                    <p>Dear <strong><t t-out=\"ctx.get('user_name')\"></t></strong>,</p>\n"
"\n"
"                    <p>An activity has been assigned to you on the lead <strong>\"<t t-out=\"ctx.get('lead_name')\"></t>\"</strong> (Stage: <t t-out=\"ctx.get('stage_name')\"></t>).</p>\n"
"\n"
"                    <div style=\"background-color: #f8f9fa; border-left: 4px solid #007bff; padding: 15px; margin: 20px 0;\">\n"
"                        <p style=\"margin: 0;\"><strong>Activity:</strong> <t t-out=\"ctx.get('activity_name')\"></t></p>\n"
"                        <p style=\"margin: 5px 0 0 0;\"><strong>Due Date:</strong> <t t-out=\"ctx.get('due_date')\"></t></p>\n"
"                    </div>\n"
"\n"
"                    <p>Kindly ensure this activity is completed by the due date to maintain workflow efficiency.</p>\n"
"\n"
"                    <div style=\"margin-top: 30px; padding-top: 20px; border-top: 1px solid #eee;\">\n"
"                        <p style=\"margin: 0;\">Best regards,</p>\n"
"                        <p style=\"margin: 5px 0 0 0;\"><strong>CRM Team</strong></p>\n"
"                        <t t-if=\"object.company_id.name\">\n"
"                            <p style=\"margin: 5px 0 0 0; color: #666; font-size: 14px;\">\n"
"                                <t t-out=\"object.company_id.name\"></t>\n"
"                            </p>\n"
"                        </t>\n"
"                    </div>\n"
"                </div>\n"
"            "
msgstr ""
"<div style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; line-height: 1.6; color: #333;\">\n"
"                    <div style=\"border-bottom: 2px solid #007bff; padding-bottom: 10px; margin-bottom: 20px;\">\n"
"                        <h2 style=\"color: #007bff; margin: 0;\">Activiteit toegewezen aan lead</h2>\n"
"                    </div>\n"
"\n"
"                    <p>Beste <strong><t t-out=\"ctx.get('user_name')\"></t></strong>,</p>\n"
"\n"
"                    <p>Er is een activiteit aan u toegewezen voor de lead <strong>\"<t t-out=\"ctx.get('lead_name')\"></t>\"</strong> (Fase: <t t-out=\"ctx.get('stage_name')\"></t>).</p>\n"
"\n"
"                    <div style=\"background-color: #f8f9fa; border-left: 4px solid #007bff; padding: 15px; margin: 20px 0;\">\n"
"                        <p style=\"margin: 0;\"><strong>Activiteit:</strong> <t t-out=\"ctx.get('activity_name')\"></t></p>\n"
"                        <p style=\"margin: 5px 0 0 0;\"><strong>Vervaldatum:</strong> <t t-out=\"ctx.get('due_date')\"></t></p>\n"
"                    </div>\n"
"\n"
"                    <p>Zorg ervoor dat deze activiteit vóór de vervaldatum wordt voltooid om de efficiëntie van de workflow te behouden.</p>\n"
"\n"
"                    <div style=\"margin-top: 30px; padding-top: 20px; border-top: 1px solid #eee;\">\n"
"                        <p style=\"margin: 0;\">Met vriendelijke groet,</p>\n"
"                        <p style=\"margin: 5px 0 0 0;\"><strong>CRM-team</strong></p>\n"
"                        <t t-if=\"object.company_id.name\">\n"
"                            <p style=\"margin: 5px 0 0 0; color: #666; font-size: 14px;\">\n"
"                                <t t-out=\"object.company_id.name\"></t>\n"
"                            </p>\n"
"                        </t>\n"
"                    </div>\n"
"                </div>\n"
"            "

#. module: cyllo_crm
#: model:mail.template,body_html:cyllo_crm.crm_subscription_report_email_template
msgid ""
"<div>\n"
"                    <p>Hi <t t-esc=\"object.user_id.name\"></t>,</p>\n"
"\n"
"                    <p>\n"
"                        Your scheduled subscription report\n"
"                        <strong>\"<t t-esc=\"object.name.title()\"></t>\"</strong>has been generated.\n"
"                    </p>\n"
"\n"
"                    <p>\n"
"                        <strong>Report Frequency:</strong>\n"
"                        <t t-esc=\"object.frequency.title()\"></t>\n"
"                        <br>\n"
"                    </p>\n"
"\n"
"                    <p>\n"
"                        Please find the report attached with this email.\n"
"                    </p>\n"
"\n"
"                    <p style=\"margin-top: 20px;\">\n"
"                        Best regards,\n"
"                        <br>\n"
"                        <strong>\n"
"                            <t t-esc=\"object.company_id.name\"></t>\n"
"                        </strong>\n"
"                    </p>\n"
"                </div>\n"
"            "
msgstr ""
"<div>\n"
"                    <p>Hallo <t t-esc=\"object.user_id.name\"></t>,</p>\n"
"\n"
"                    <p>\n"
"                        Uw geplande abonnementsrapport\n"
"                        <strong>\"<t t-esc=\"object.name.title()\"></t>\"</strong> is gegenereerd.\n"
"                    </p>\n"
"\n"
"                    <p>\n"
"                        <strong>Rapportfrequentie:</strong>\n"
"                        <t t-esc=\"object.frequency.title()\"></t>\n"
"                        <br>\n"
"                    </p>\n"
"\n"
"                    <p>\n"
"                        Het rapport is bij deze e-mail gevoegd.\n"
"                    </p>\n"
"\n"
"                    <p style=\"margin-top: 20px;\">\n"
"                        Met vriendelijke groet,\n"
"                        <br>\n"
"                        <strong>\n"
"                            <t t-esc=\"object.company_id.name\"></t>\n"
"                        </strong>\n"
"                    </p>\n"
"                </div>\n"
"            "

#. module: cyllo_crm
#: model:mail.template,body_html:cyllo_crm.deal_reminder
msgid ""
"<div>\n"
"                   <p>\n"
"                       Hello\n"
"                       <t t-out=\"object.user_id.name\"></t>,\n"
"                       <br>\n"
"                       <br>\n"
"                       The lead \"<t t-out=\"object.name\"></t>\" assigned to you has been idle for a while.\n"
"                   <br>\n"
"                        🔹 Lead Name: <t t-out=\"object.name\"></t>\n"
"                       <br>\n"
"                        🔹 Customer:  <t t-out=\"object.partner_id.name\"></t>\n"
"                       <br>\n"
"                        🔹 Last Activity: <t t-out=\"object.last_stage_update_date\"></t>\n"
"                       <br>\n"
"                        🔹 Days Since Last Update: <t t-out=\"object.lead_idle_days\"></t>\n"
"                       <br>\n"
"                       <br>\n"
"\n"
"Please take the necessary action to follow up. If this lead is no longer relevant, consider updating its status.\n"
"                       <br>\n"
"                       <br>\n"
"                       <br>\n"
"                       <br>\n"
"                       Thanks and regards\n"
"                   </p>\n"
"               </div>\n"
"           "
msgstr ""
"<div>\n"
"                   <p>\n"
"                       Hallo\n"
"                       <t t-out=\"object.user_id.name\"></t>,\n"
"                       <br>\n"
"                       <br>\n"
"                       De lead \"<t t-out=\"object.name\"></t>\" die aan u is toegewezen, is al een tijdje inactief.\n"
"                   <br>\n"
"                        🔹 Leadnaam: <t t-out=\"object.name\"></t>\n"
"                       <br>\n"
"                        🔹 Klant:  <t t-out=\"object.partner_id.name\"></t>\n"
"                       <br>\n"
"                        🔹 Laatste activiteit: <t t-out=\"object.last_stage_update_date\"></t>\n"
"                       <br>\n"
"                        🔹 Dagen sinds laatste update: <t t-out=\"object.lead_idle_days\"></t>\n"
"                       <br>\n"
"                       <br>\n"
"\n"
"Neem de nodige actie om op te volgen. Als deze lead niet langer relevant is, overweeg dan de status bij te werken.\n"
"                       <br>\n"
"                       <br>\n"
"                       <br>\n"
"                       <br>\n"
"                       Bedankt en vriendelijke groet,\n"
"                   </p>\n"
"               </div>\n"
"           "

